name: IsItWednesdayMyDudes
0:
”Alexa, is it Wednesday my dudes?”
”Alexa, tell is it Wednesday my dudes hi”
”Alexa, tell is it Wednesday my dudes hello world”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: is it wednesday my dudes
des: Have you ever wondered, is it Wednesday? Now you can (you already could) ask Alexa and it'll tell you! Just add "my dudes" to the end of your question and Alexa will respond with character, style, and poise. If it's not Wednesday, it'll still tell you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
